You have arrived at the second scene!

* temp answer, false
* temp tries, 3

* while tries > 0 and !answer
	Do you want to go back to the start?
	* choice
		# Yes, take me back!
			* set answer, true
		# Not yet...
			* set tries, tries - 1
			* if tries > 0
				Okay, but you only have ${tries} chances left.

* if answer
	Great choice!
* else
	Fine, staying here then.

* flush

* goto_scene startup
